# Caddy auto-provisions a Let's Encrypt TLS cert for this domain and reverse
# proxies to the Aria app. WebSocket upgrades (/api/offer signaling responses
# and /telephony/ws) are handled automatically by Caddy v2.
#
# Prerequisite: an A record for aria.vaticanninfra.in must point at this
# droplet's public IP BEFORE starting Caddy, or cert issuance will fail.
aria.vaticanninfra.in {
	reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:7860
}
